'''约翰·西蒙·古根海姆纪念基金会'''（{{lang-en|John Simon Guggenheim Memorial Foundation}}）是由奥尔加·古根海姆（{{lang|en|Olga Guggenheim}}）和[[西蒙·古根海姆|西蒙·古根海姆]]（{{lang|en|Simon Guggenheim}}）夫妇在1925年建立的基金会<ref name="bloomberg">{{cite web | url = http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=4932668 | accessdate = 18 November 2014 | publisher = [[Bloomberg_Businessweek|Bloomberg Businessweek]] | title = Company Overview of John Simon Guggenheim Memorial Foundation | archive-date = 2014-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129032340/http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=4932668 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，以纪念二人在1922年4月26日去世的儿子约翰·西蒙·古根海姆（{{lang|en|John Simon Guggenheim}}）<ref>{{cite news|accessdate=2018-12-04|title=Mrs. Simon Guggenheim Dead; Philanthropist and Arts Patron|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1970/02/16/archives/mrs-simon-guggenheim-dead-philanthropist-and-arts-patron.html|newspaper=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808005806/https://www.nytimes.com/1970/02/16/archives/mrs-simon-guggenheim-dead-philanthropist-and-arts-patron.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。基金会每年颁发[[古根海姆獎|古根海姆獎]]，以鼓励自然科学、社会科学、人文科学等领域的重要贡献<ref name="bloomberg" />。
